@startuml
title Sequence diagram (richiesta personalizzata) - Iterazione 2

actor User as U
participant "Frontend"          as FE
participant "API Gateway"       as GW
participant "JWT Manager"       as JWT
participant "Orchestrator"      as Orch
participant "Profile Repository" as PR
participant "MongoDB"           as DB
participant "Classifier"        as Cls
participant "Generator"         as Gen
participant "Revision"          as Rev

U   -> FE   : Send question + JWT
FE  -> GW   : Request
GW  -> JWT  : validateToken()
JWT --> GW  : valid

GW   -> Orch : forward request
Orch -> PR   : findById()
PR   -> DB   : query
DB   --> PR  : user data
PR   --> Orch : profile

Orch -> Cls  : classify()
Cls  --> Orch : intent

Orch -> Gen  : generate(profile + question)
Gen  --> Orch : draft response

Orch -> Rev  : review()
Rev  --> Orch : final response

Orch --> GW : response
GW   --> FE : response

@enduml